==English==

===Noun===
'''encroachment''' (''plural:'' '''[[encroachments]]''')
# An [[entry]] into a place or area that was previously uncommon; an [[advance]] beyond former borders; [[intrusion]]; [[incursion]].
# An [[intrusion]] upon another's [[possession]]s or [[right]]s; [[infringement]].
# That which is [[gain]]ed by such [[unlawful]] intrusion.
# {{law}} An [[unlawful]] [[diminution]] of the [[possession]]s of another.

